  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 3</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 17 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 5 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 17</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mas, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique is learned for a specific stance, and can only be used while in the stance it was learned for. It can be learned multiple times, choosing a different stance to apply it to each time. You gain a +2 competence bonus to the Learn check if you learn this technique while you already know it. Mastery applies only to a single instance of the technique: it must be learned separately for each stance.<br><br>You make a convincing feint, provoking an attack of opportunity from the target against which you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Defense. If the target misses, you may make an attack of opportunity against them.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> Each step lowers the armor check penalty of your worn armor by 1 when determining the chance to fail to perform this technique.<br><br>The first, third and fifth steps each increase the circumstance bonus to Defense by +1.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
